Inside/Out is a collection of photographs of my home in suburban Cleveland, Ohio, begun during self-isolation with Covid-19. The series is about everyday transgressions, incursions, and boundary crossingsâ€“specifically of "nature" into "domestic" space and of non-human, viral pathogens into human bodies.
